WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Welcome to the Zink app,

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:05.000
your all-in-one music, video, and social experience.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Stream your favorite tunes with Spotify integration.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:11.000
Watch videos with a modern video player.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Stay connected with voice and video calls.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Enjoy radio stations from around the world.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:20.000
And share feedback to help us improve.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Thank you for choosing Zink.
 